text: Welcome Home Roscoe Jenkins is a 2008 American comedy movie directed by Malcolm D. Lee and starring Martin Lawrence, Joy Bryant, James Earl Jones, Margaret Avery, Mike Epps, Mo'Nique, Cedric the Entertainer, Nicole Ari Parker, Michael Clarke Duncan, Louis C.K.. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. == Other websites == * * * * Category:2008 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies directed by Malcolm D.
